title: NFL Week 13 Picks Against the Spread, Cowboys contenders? (Football 11/30)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Bryant McFadden to break down the Cowboys win over the Saints and whether or not we can buy into Dallas as a contender (3:00) and what this means for the Saints moving forward (14:00). Then Pete Prisco and R.J. White hop on the phone to make picks against the spread for every game in Week 13.
